    "Title": "DEAD SAINTS - ~mission(ReputationRank) Rank - ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Cargo Haul",
    "DisplayTitle": "DEAD SAINTS - Rookie Rank - Medium Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "If you've got a fast ship, can discreetly carry size <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> containers, and love getting a huge payout, we need you to head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> immediately and take what you find there to these drop points:\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)  \n\nThe buyers are paying a premium to get their hands on fresh stormwal meat. Stay sharp. If security catches you with this, it's your ass on the line. If you're smart, you'll use a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded up quick. \n\n-Twitch",
    "DisplayDescription": "If you've got a fast ship, can discreetly carry size <EM4>8 SCU</EM4> containers, and love getting a huge payout, we need you to head to <EM4>Orison</EM4> immediately and take what you find there to these drop points:\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER) \n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination1|Address]</EM4>  \n\nThe buyers are paying a premium to get their hands on fresh stormwal meat. Stay sharp. If security catches you with this, it's your ass on the line. If you're smart, you'll use a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to get everything loaded up quick. \n\n-Twitch",
